---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Journal — Don't Lose Your Way" description="Reflections, stories, and words for the quiet moments.">

  <section class="journal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Journal</h1>
      <p class="journal-subtitle">Words for the quiet moments.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container journal-body">
      <div class="journal-intro">
        <p>Sometimes you don't need advice. You just need to read something that makes you feel less alone.</p>
        <p>The Journal is a collection of reflections, stories, and thoughts for those moments. Updated regularly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="journal-entries">
        <article class="entry">
          <div class="entry-tag">Reflection</div>
          <h2 class="entry-title">The Weight of Silence</h2>
          <p class="entry-excerpt">For 34 years, I didn't speak. Not because I had nothing to say, but because I didn't know how. Silence isn't empty — it's heavy. And the heaviest silences are the ones we carry alone.</p>
          <span class="entry-date">May 2026</span>
        </article>

        <article class="entry">
          <div class="entry-tag">Reflection</div>
          <h2 class="entry-title">Don't Lose Your Way</h2>
          <p class="entry-excerpt">Those four words carry more weight than any business plan, any revenue target, any metric. They came from a father to a son. And now they belong to everyone who needs them.</p>
          <span class="entry-date">May 2026</span>
        </article>

        <article class="entry">
          <div class="entry-tag">Music</div>
          <h2 class="entry-title">When Words Aren't Enough</h2>
          <p class="entry-excerpt">Sometimes a song says what words can't. The Chapel turns feelings into sound — because not everything needs to be explained. Some things just need to be heard.</p>
          <span class="entry-date">May 2026</span>
        </article>
      </div>

      <div class="journal-cta">
        <p>More entries coming soon.</p>
        <a href="/chapel" class="cta">Visit the Chapel</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>
  .journal-hero {
    padding: 8rem 0 2rem;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .journal-hero h1 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .journal-subtitle {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
  }

  .journal-body {
    max-width: 40rem;
  }

  .journal-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .journal-intro p {
    font-size: 1rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .journal-entries {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .entry {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.75rem;
  }

  .entry-tag {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 0.6875rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    background: rgba(168,85,247,0.1);
    padding: 0.25rem 0.75rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .entry-title {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .entry-excerpt {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-weight: 300;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .entry-date {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
  }

  .journal-cta {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .journal-cta p {
    color: var(--color-text-subtle);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .cta {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.75rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 9999px;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: white;
    transition: all 0.25s;
  }

  .cta:hover { background: var(--color-accent-2); }
</style>